11#import "RTCVideoDecoderFactoryH264.h"
12
13#import "RTCH264ProfileLevelId.h"
14#import "RTCVideoDecoderH264.h"
15
16@implementation RTCVideoDecoderFactoryH264
17
18- (NSArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *)supportedCodecs {
19 NSMutableArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *codecs = [NSMutableArray array];
20 NSString *codecName = kRTCVideoCodecH264Name;
21
22 NSDictionary<NSString *, NSString *> *constrainedHighParams = @{
23 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedHigh,
24 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
25 @"packetization-mode" : @"1",
26 };
27 RTCVideoCodecInfo *constrainedHighInfo =
28 [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:codecName parameters:constrainedHighParams];
29 [codecs addObject:constrainedHighInfo];
30
31 NSDictionary<NSString *, NSString *> *constrainedBaselineParams = @{
32 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedBaseline,
33 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
34 @"packetization-mode" : @"1",
35 };
36 RTCVideoCodecInfo *constrainedBaselineInfo =
37 [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:codecName parameters:constrainedBaselineParams];
38 [codecs addObject:constrainedBaselineInfo];
39
40 return [codecs copy];
41}
42
43- (id<RTCVideoDecoder>)createDecoder:(RTCVideoCodecInfo *)info {
44 return [[RTCVideoDecoderH264 alloc] init];
45}
46
47@end
